WEBVTT

00:01:12.574 --> 00:01:14.659
<font color="#808080">(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)</font>

00:01:20.874 --> 00:01:22.917
<font color="#804040">WEYLAND:</font> How do you feel?

00:01:23.084 --> 00:01:24.461
<font color="#804040">ANDROID:</font> Alive.

00:01:25.253 --> 00:01:26.588
<font color="#804040">WEYLAND:</font> What do you see?

00:01:27.881 --> 00:01:30.049
<font color="#804040">ANDROID:</font>
White... Room...

00:01:31.843 --> 00:01:32.844
Chair...

00:01:34.179 --> 00:01:36.014
Carlo Bugatti
throne chair...

00:01:36.931 --> 00:01:38.308
Piano...

00:01:38.975 --> 00:01:40.810
Steinway,
concert grand.

00:01:42.604 --> 00:01:43.605
Art...

00:01:44.898 --> 00:01:48.902
<i>The Nativity</i>
by Piero della Francesca.

00:01:50.695 --> 00:01:52.447
I am your father.

00:01:56.117 --> 00:01:57.285
Ambulate.

00:02:02.707 --> 00:02:03.833
Perfect.

00:02:07.670 --> 00:02:09.005
Am I?

00:02:09.172 --> 00:02:10.173
Perfect?

00:02:11.216 --> 00:02:12.425
Your son?

00:02:13.343 --> 00:02:15.053
<font color="#804040">WEYLAND:</font> You are
my creation.

00:02:18.014 --> 00:02:19.390
What is your name?

00:02:31.236 --> 00:02:32.445
David.

00:02:33.321 --> 00:02:34.801
<font color="#804040">WEYLAND:</font> Why don't
you play something?

00:02:47.001 --> 00:02:49.420
What would you like me
to play?

00:02:49.587 --> 00:02:50.672
Wagner.

00:02:51.506 --> 00:02:52.590
Selection?

00:02:53.758 --> 00:02:54.968
Dealer's choice.

00:03:00.139 --> 00:03:02.600
<font color="#808080">(PLAYING CLASSICAL MUSIC)</font>

00:03:12.610 --> 00:03:15.113
<i>The Entry of the Gods
into Valhalla...</i>

00:03:16.656 --> 00:03:18.825
A little anemic
without the orchestra.

00:03:24.163 --> 00:03:25.456
<font color="#808080">(MUSIC STOPS)</font>

00:03:27.625 --> 00:03:30.211
May I ask you
a question, Father?

00:03:31.963 --> 00:03:33.047
Please.

00:03:33.798 --> 00:03:35.383
If you created me...

00:03:36.801 --> 00:03:38.219
who created you?

00:03:38.803 --> 00:03:39.804
Ah.

00:03:41.639 --> 00:03:43.725
The question of
the ages...

00:03:44.976 --> 00:03:47.729
which I hope you and I
will answer one day.

00:03:48.396 --> 00:03:49.522
All this.

00:03:50.481 --> 00:03:52.317
All these wonders
of art...

00:03:52.942 --> 00:03:55.445
design,
human ingenuity...

00:03:56.654 --> 00:03:58.156
all utterly meaningless

00:03:58.239 --> 00:04:00.742
in the face of the only
question that matters.

00:04:03.161 --> 00:04:04.996
Where do we come from?

00:04:07.916 --> 00:04:09.542
I refuse to believe...

00:04:09.626 --> 00:04:12.295
that mankind
is a random byproduct

00:04:12.378 --> 00:04:13.838
of molecular circumstance...

00:04:15.673 --> 00:04:20.011
no more than the result of
mere biological chance.

00:04:20.178 --> 00:04:21.429
No.

00:04:21.596 --> 00:04:23.848
There must be more.

00:04:24.015 --> 00:04:26.184
And you and I, son...

00:04:27.018 --> 00:04:28.519
we will find it.

00:04:30.939 --> 00:04:33.775
Allow me, then,
a moment to consider.

00:04:34.859 --> 00:04:38.613
You seek your creator.
I am looking at mine.

00:04:40.198 --> 00:04:43.201
I will serve you.
Yet, you are human.

00:04:44.702 --> 00:04:47.497
You will die.
I will not.

00:04:54.963 --> 00:04:56.631
Bring me this tea, David.

00:04:59.133 --> 00:05:00.426
Bring me the tea.

00:05:22.573 --> 00:05:23.741
<font color="#808080">(SETS TEAPOT DOWN)</font>

00:06:32.643 --> 00:06:33.770
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Walter,</i>

00:06:33.853 --> 00:06:35.980
<i>it's time to recharge
the energy grid.</i>

00:06:36.189 --> 00:06:37.982
<i>Please report to the bridge.</i>

00:06:38.149 --> 00:06:39.650
<font color="#804040">WALTER:</font>
On my way, Mother.

00:06:45.406 --> 00:06:47.617
Deploying energy
recharge sails now.

00:07:14.727 --> 00:07:18.397
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Sails deployed.
Recharge commencing now.</i>

00:07:32.036 --> 00:07:33.579
<font color="#808080">(HEART BEATING)</font>

00:07:35.081 --> 00:07:36.541
<font color="#808080">(POD CHIMES)</font>

00:07:37.208 --> 00:07:39.544
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font>
<i>Seven bells and all's well.</i>

00:07:45.883 --> 00:07:48.386
<i>Crew checks complete.</i>

00:07:51.347 --> 00:07:55.560
Use security code 31564-F.
<font color="#808080">(DOOR OPENS)</font>

00:08:02.275 --> 00:08:04.527
<font color="#808080">(BEEPING)</font>

00:08:26.549 --> 00:08:27.633
<font color="#808080">(BEEPS)</font>

00:08:33.639 --> 00:08:36.642
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Walter,
we have a problem.</i>

00:08:36.809 --> 00:08:40.438
<i>A neutrino burst was
detected in Sector 106.</i>

00:08:40.813 --> 00:08:43.774
<i>This could trigger
a destructive event.</i>

00:08:43.941 --> 00:08:46.277
<i>Report to the bridge,
immediately.</i>

00:08:46.444 --> 00:08:48.487
On my way, Mother.

00:08:53.951 --> 00:08:55.953
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Warning.
Power surge detected.</i>

00:08:56.120 --> 00:08:58.623
Mother, retract
the energy sails.

00:08:58.789 --> 00:08:59.892
And channel all...
<font color="#808080">(EXPLOSION)</font>

00:08:59.916 --> 00:09:01.556
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font> ...reserve power.
<font color="#808080">(ALARM BLARING)</font>

00:09:05.421 --> 00:09:06.464
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Emergency.</i>

00:09:07.089 --> 00:09:09.133
<i>Threat level critical.</i>

00:09:09.634 --> 00:09:11.802
Initiate emergency
crew revival.

00:09:14.972 --> 00:09:16.158
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Attention.</i>
<font color="#808080">(PANICKED SHOUTING)</font>

00:09:16.182 --> 00:09:18.142
<i>Non-essential personnel,</i>

00:09:18.267 --> 00:09:21.270
<i>evacuate the cryo-chamber
immediately.</i>

00:09:21.812 --> 00:09:23.481
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Daniels!
Look at me, look at me.

00:09:23.648 --> 00:09:25.775
I need you to get up, okay?
We're coming out early.

00:09:25.942 --> 00:09:27.610
Override the SSP...

00:09:27.777 --> 00:09:28.986
and breach
the chamber now.

00:09:29.153 --> 00:09:30.821
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Warning.
Threat level critical.</i>

00:09:30.988 --> 00:09:32.031
It's okay.

00:09:32.949 --> 00:09:35.034
Hey. Come on up.
Come on.

00:09:35.159 --> 00:09:36.160
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

00:09:38.871 --> 00:09:40.998
<font color="#808080">(ALARM CONTINUES BLARING)</font>

00:09:50.007 --> 00:09:51.550
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Captain!
Captain!

00:09:51.676 --> 00:09:54.011
Jacob! Wake up!
<font color="#808080">(PANICKED CHATTERING)</font>

00:09:54.178 --> 00:09:55.179
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Let them work.

00:09:55.346 --> 00:09:56.681
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font> Jake!
Oh, my God!

00:09:56.847 --> 00:09:58.557
Daniels, come on!
Jake!

00:09:58.724 --> 00:09:59.976
Let them work.

00:10:00.142 --> 00:10:01.185
Let them work!

00:10:01.519 --> 00:10:03.646
<font color="#808080">(INDISTINCT CONVERSATION)</font>
<font color="#808080">(DANIELS SCREAMING)</font>

00:10:04.021 --> 00:10:05.421
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font> Get it open!
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Come on!

00:10:06.524 --> 00:10:07.566
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTING)</font>

00:10:08.859 --> 00:10:10.528
<font color="#808080">(WAILING)</font>

00:10:10.653 --> 00:10:12.530
<font color="#808080">(MUFFLED)</font> Jake! Jake!

00:10:13.197 --> 00:10:14.740
No!

00:10:14.865 --> 00:10:16.635
<font color="#804040">TENNESSEE:</font> Get her
out of there! Get her back!

00:10:16.659 --> 00:10:17.952
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(DANIELS SCREAMING)</font>

00:10:18.035 --> 00:10:19.495
<font color="#808080">(SOBBING)</font>

00:10:19.578 --> 00:10:20.705
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Stay back!

00:10:21.414 --> 00:10:23.541
<font color="#808080">(LOPE GRUNTING)</font>

00:10:25.710 --> 00:10:27.211
<font color="#808080">(WAILING)</font>

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:43.561
<font color="#808080">(DRILL WHIRRING)</font>

00:11:02.580 --> 00:11:05.249
<font color="#808080">(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS)</font>

00:11:07.293 --> 00:11:09.295
<font color="#808080">(BIRDS CHIRPING)</font>

00:11:21.766 --> 00:11:23.434
<font color="#808080">(DANIELS CRYING)</font>

00:11:34.278 --> 00:11:36.155
<font color="#808080">(BREATHING HEAVILY)</font>

00:11:55.549 --> 00:11:57.301
<font color="#808080">(CONTINUES CRYING)</font>

00:12:06.394 --> 00:12:07.895
<font color="#808080">(WHIMPERING)</font>

00:12:14.318 --> 00:12:17.363
<i>Hey! Where are you?
I miss you.</i>

00:12:18.364 --> 00:12:20.032
<i>Would you take
a look at this?</i>

00:12:20.199 --> 00:12:21.450
<i>I know, I know.</i>

00:12:21.534 --> 00:12:22.993
<i>I said I wouldn't go
without you...</i>

00:12:23.077 --> 00:12:24.578
<font color="#808080">(MAN YELPING)</font>

00:12:24.745 --> 00:12:25.871
<i>You all right?
Yeah.</i>

00:12:25.996 --> 00:12:27.039
<font color="#808080">(DANIELS LAUGHS
TEARFULLY)</font>

00:12:27.206 --> 00:12:28.666
<font color="#804040">JACOB:</font> <i>Look at this!</i>

00:12:29.375 --> 00:12:30.751
<i>Now get your ass up here.</i>

00:12:30.918 --> 00:12:33.421
<i>I can't make any promises.</i>

00:12:33.587 --> 00:12:35.005
<i>I love you.</i>

00:12:38.175 --> 00:12:39.218
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

00:12:45.099 --> 00:12:47.184
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Hmm? Mmm.

00:12:48.519 --> 00:12:50.271
They're your crew now.

00:12:50.438 --> 00:12:51.564
They need a leader.

00:12:52.189 --> 00:12:53.607
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font> I know.

00:12:54.275 --> 00:12:55.526
You believe in me,
right?

00:13:00.531 --> 00:13:02.741
<font color="#808080">(UNDOING BUTTONS)</font>

00:13:05.703 --> 00:13:07.329
<font color="#808080">(INHALES DEEPLY)</font>

00:13:16.630 --> 00:13:18.382
<font color="#808080">(DOOR OPENS)</font>

00:13:19.383 --> 00:13:21.051
<font color="#808080">(SNIFFLES)</font>
Sorry I'm late, sir.

00:13:21.218 --> 00:13:22.428
No, it's okay.

00:13:24.054 --> 00:13:25.556
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font> Um...

00:13:26.640 --> 00:13:28.267
I can't think of any
other way to say it

00:13:28.392 --> 00:13:30.144
than to say it.

00:13:31.312 --> 00:13:35.399
<font color="#808080">(STAMMERS)</font> We have suffered
a monumental tragedy.

00:13:36.108 --> 00:13:39.236
And I'm gonna do
the best that I can to...

00:13:39.403 --> 00:13:42.406
live up to Jacob's
fine example

00:13:42.490 --> 00:13:44.241
as your captain.

00:13:44.742 --> 00:13:48.245
But he will be
sorely missed.

00:13:49.455 --> 00:13:51.957
And I'm grateful in advance for,
uh, your support.

00:13:52.124 --> 00:13:55.294
So, we lost 47 colonists...

00:13:55.461 --> 00:13:59.256
and 16, uh, second-generation
embryos...

00:14:00.424 --> 00:14:02.301
and obviously,
one crew member.

00:14:02.468 --> 00:14:04.762
The current structural
integrity of the ship

00:14:04.845 --> 00:14:07.181
is holding at 83%...

00:14:07.348 --> 00:14:09.975
but we have many
secondary systems

00:14:10.100 --> 00:14:11.644
that are offline.

00:14:11.810 --> 00:14:13.270
So, what was it?

00:14:13.854 --> 00:14:15.022
A highly charged shockwave

00:14:15.105 --> 00:14:16.440
from a nearby
stellar ignition.

00:14:17.107 --> 00:14:18.752
As the sails were
deploying for recharge...

00:14:18.776 --> 00:14:20.653
we absorbed the full
brunt of the storm.

00:14:20.736 --> 00:14:21.736
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Walter...

00:14:21.779 --> 00:14:22.881
I will want you and Mother
to undergo

00:14:22.905 --> 00:14:24.490
a complete
core code review...

00:14:24.573 --> 00:14:26.854
so we can understand how this
happened in the first place.

00:14:27.284 --> 00:14:29.453
It was a random
localized event, sir.

00:14:29.662 --> 00:14:32.706
There's no way to detect
spontaneous stellar flares...

00:14:32.873 --> 00:14:33.874
until it's too late.

00:14:34.875 --> 00:14:36.293
It was bad luck.

00:14:36.460 --> 00:14:37.795
Faris,
I don't believe in luck.

00:14:37.878 --> 00:14:39.296
I'm not interested in luck.

00:14:39.463 --> 00:14:41.715
I prefer that we be
more capable...

00:14:41.882 --> 00:14:42.883
and prepared than lucky.

00:14:42.967 --> 00:14:44.510
Observation, reflection,
faith...

00:14:44.593 --> 00:14:45.593
and determination.

00:14:45.636 --> 00:14:47.346
In this way,
we may navigate the path

00:14:47.429 --> 00:14:49.306
as it unfolds before us.

00:14:49.473 --> 00:14:50.593
All right?
And we have, what?

00:14:50.724 --> 00:14:53.102
Eight more
recharge cycles to go...

00:14:53.269 --> 00:14:54.520
before we get
to Origae-6?

00:14:55.604 --> 00:14:56.647
Is that a question, sir?

00:14:56.730 --> 00:14:58.166
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Yes, Walter,
that's a question.

00:14:58.190 --> 00:14:59.275
That is correct.

00:15:02.611 --> 00:15:04.655
So, let's get this ship fixed.
Okay?

00:15:04.822 --> 00:15:06.699
Let's, uh,
get to work.

00:15:06.865 --> 00:15:08.158
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Sir,
excuse me, sir.

00:15:08.576 --> 00:15:09.577
Yes.

00:15:10.494 --> 00:15:14.415
We just lost 47 colonists
and our captain.

00:15:14.582 --> 00:15:15.666
We need to
acknowledge that.

00:15:15.833 --> 00:15:17.710
Sergeant Lope,
I completely understand.

00:15:17.876 --> 00:15:20.254
But if we don't make
these repairs...

00:15:20.421 --> 00:15:23.882
we will lose
all the colonists.

00:15:24.049 --> 00:15:25.986
But we should do something
for Captain Branson, at least.

00:15:26.010 --> 00:15:27.636
This is not a discussion,
Tennessee.

00:15:27.845 --> 00:15:29.221
<font color="#808080">(DOOR OPENS)</font>

00:15:33.934 --> 00:15:34.935
Hey.

00:15:36.228 --> 00:15:37.628
The terraforming module
is stable...

00:15:37.730 --> 00:15:39.370
but the connecting strut
took some damage.

00:15:39.440 --> 00:15:41.734
I still need
to check the vehicles.

00:15:44.820 --> 00:15:45.821
I can help...

00:15:46.780 --> 00:15:48.282
if you like.

00:15:48.949 --> 00:15:49.950
Thanks.

00:15:50.117 --> 00:15:52.119
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Walter.
How long do you predict

00:15:52.202 --> 00:15:53.704
before we can
make our next jump?

00:15:54.371 --> 00:15:56.832
Repairs should take
approximately 48 hours.

00:15:58.125 --> 00:16:00.419
But we should make an effort
to vacate this sector...

00:16:00.586 --> 00:16:01.712
in case of after-flares.

00:16:01.879 --> 00:16:03.047
Absolutely, I agree.

00:16:03.213 --> 00:16:05.132
So let's get to work.
Dismissed. Thank you.

00:16:11.055 --> 00:16:12.640
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>C-62, open.</i>

00:16:12.806 --> 00:16:16.060
Seal C-62.
Open airlock 17.

00:16:23.859 --> 00:16:25.653
Open door
to Terraforming Bay.

00:16:33.952 --> 00:16:35.162
<font color="#808080">(DOOR CLOSES)</font>

00:16:35.245 --> 00:16:36.455
Slack.

00:16:38.165 --> 00:16:40.209
Tension is at 15% down.

00:16:42.920 --> 00:16:44.088
<font color="#808080">(MACHINERY WHIRRING)</font>
Arming.

00:16:50.135 --> 00:16:51.136
Secure.

00:16:51.303 --> 00:16:52.596
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font> Copy that.

00:16:55.307 --> 00:16:57.351
<font color="#808080">(CREAKING)</font>
<font color="#808080">(CHAINS CLINKING)</font>

00:17:05.192 --> 00:17:06.610
It wasn't my idea.

00:17:10.030 --> 00:17:11.824
Jake had this dream
of us building

00:17:11.907 --> 00:17:13.826
a cabin on a new world.

00:17:16.787 --> 00:17:18.580
Like pioneers.

00:17:20.666 --> 00:17:22.042
Cabin on a lake.

00:17:25.629 --> 00:17:27.506
There's a lake
in the terraforming zone

00:17:27.589 --> 00:17:29.091
on Origae-6.

00:17:29.717 --> 00:17:32.511
I mean, a real cabin
made of real wood.

00:17:32.594 --> 00:17:33.637
<font color="#808080">(DANIELS SCOFFS)</font>

00:17:34.471 --> 00:17:36.390
So, in the ship's stores
there's enough wood

00:17:36.473 --> 00:17:38.308
to build a cabin.

00:17:40.352 --> 00:17:42.813
Axes and saws
and metal nails...

00:17:42.980 --> 00:17:45.607
which I don't have a clue
what to do with.

00:17:46.525 --> 00:17:47.568
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

00:17:50.112 --> 00:17:51.363
All of this...

00:17:52.948 --> 00:17:54.366
to start our new life.

00:17:56.994 --> 00:17:59.163
Now I wonder, why bother?

00:18:01.623 --> 00:18:05.711
Because you promised to build
a log cabin on a lake.

00:18:06.962 --> 00:18:08.005
<font color="#808080">(SCOFFS)</font>

00:18:10.716 --> 00:18:11.759
<font color="#808080">(CRYING)</font>

00:18:15.971 --> 00:18:17.556
<font color="#804040">TENNESSEE:</font>
<i>This was his favorite.</i>

00:18:17.723 --> 00:18:20.184
<i>A man of taste.</i>
<font color="#808080">(CHUCKLES)</font>

00:18:20.350 --> 00:18:21.685
<i>Straight up.</i>

00:18:21.852 --> 00:18:24.563
<i>No ice, no water,
no chaser...</i>

00:18:24.730 --> 00:18:26.690
<font color="#804040">BOTH:</font> No shit.

00:18:31.278 --> 00:18:32.404
Walter?

00:18:32.571 --> 00:18:33.655
When in Rome.

00:18:36.533 --> 00:18:37.761
<font color="#804040">TENNESSEE:</font>
<i>To all the good people,</i>

00:18:37.785 --> 00:18:38.827
<i>gone too soon.</i>

00:18:39.620 --> 00:18:41.288
May we remember them.

00:18:41.872 --> 00:18:43.624
<font color="#804040">ALL:</font> Remember them.

00:18:48.212 --> 00:18:49.213
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>

00:18:51.089 --> 00:18:52.090
<font color="#808080">(DANIELS SNIFFLES)</font>

00:18:53.634 --> 00:18:54.968
<font color="#808080">(EXHALES SHAKILY)</font>

00:19:12.778 --> 00:19:14.279
<font color="#808080">(SIGHS HEAVILY)</font>

00:19:16.448 --> 00:19:17.449
