<font color="#808080">(CREW CHATTERING IN RELIEF)</font>

00:31:11.788 --> 00:31:13.623
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font>
<i>Landing sensors engaged.</i>

00:31:28.638 --> 00:31:30.473
I don't like this terrain.

00:31:30.640 --> 00:31:32.475
We've got smooth water
over there.

00:31:32.642 --> 00:31:35.228
I'm gonna put us down amphib.
Okay.

00:32:09.345 --> 00:32:10.805
<font color="#808080">(CREW EXCLAIMING)</font>
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Contact.</i>

00:32:10.972 --> 00:32:12.056
<i>Engine stop.</i>

00:32:12.140 --> 00:32:13.141
<font color="#808080">(ANKOR SIGHS IN RELIEF)</font>

00:32:14.809 --> 00:32:15.809
<font color="#804040">FARIS:</font> We're down.

00:32:15.852 --> 00:32:16.853
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Bars.

00:32:17.020 --> 00:32:18.580
<font color="#804040">UPWORTH:</font> <i>Lander One,
are you reading me?</i>

00:32:18.646 --> 00:32:20.898
Roger that. That was
one hell of a landing.

00:32:21.065 --> 00:32:22.859
Yeah. We're having
some trouble reading you.

00:32:23.026 --> 00:32:24.670
Is there any way you can try
and boost the signal?

00:32:24.694 --> 00:32:25.921
<font color="#804040">FARIS:</font> <i>We may have
clipped something</i>

00:32:25.945 --> 00:32:27.065
<i>on our way down
in the water.</i>

00:32:27.155 --> 00:32:28.323
<i>If you can hear me,</i>

00:32:28.406 --> 00:32:29.949
<i>I'm gonna check
for potential damage...</i>

00:32:30.116 --> 00:32:32.702
<i>on the hull first, and then
I will check the uplink.</i>

00:32:32.869 --> 00:32:35.705
<font color="#804040">UPWORTH:</font> <i>Well, let me know
how it looks. Over.</i>

00:32:37.373 --> 00:32:38.851
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Confirming
atmospheric composition.</i>

00:32:38.875 --> 00:32:40.418
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Here you go, big guy.

00:32:40.585 --> 00:32:41.794
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Oxygen, 19.5%.</i>

00:32:41.961 --> 00:32:43.171
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Ankor.

00:32:43.338 --> 00:32:44.881
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font> <i>Nitrogen, 79.4%.</i>

00:32:45.048 --> 00:32:46.466
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Cole.

00:32:46.549 --> 00:32:47.550
Rosie.

00:32:47.634 --> 00:32:49.135
<font color="#804040">MOTHER:</font>
<i>Barometric pressure, 15.4 PSI.</i>

00:32:49.302 --> 00:32:50.720
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Ledward.

00:32:58.811 --> 00:32:59.812
Everyone set?

00:33:02.690 --> 00:33:04.776
<font color="#804040">COLE:</font> Let's go.
Let's move.

00:33:04.901 --> 00:33:06.861
<font color="#808080">(CREW MURMURING)</font>

00:33:09.614 --> 00:33:10.615
<font color="#804040">ROSENTHAL:</font> Come on, guys.

00:33:10.698 --> 00:33:12.075
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Air feels good.
<font color="#804040">KARINE:</font> Wow.

00:33:15.119 --> 00:33:16.287
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Faris,
have you got me?

00:33:16.454 --> 00:33:17.705
<font color="#804040">FARIS:</font> <i>Yeah.
Loud and clear.</i>

00:33:18.498 --> 00:33:19.683
Okay. We're gonna
keep expedition

00:33:19.707 --> 00:33:20.875
security protocols
in place.

00:33:21.042 --> 00:33:23.920
Keep those doors
locked and sealed. Right?

00:33:24.087 --> 00:33:25.088
<font color="#804040">FARIS:</font> <i>Yeah. Copy.</i>

00:33:25.171 --> 00:33:26.255
Will do.

00:33:26.422 --> 00:33:27.965
Y'all have fun.

00:33:35.473 --> 00:33:37.100
Walter, how far
do we have to go?

00:33:39.060 --> 00:33:41.938
Signal's source
is 8 km west...

00:33:42.105 --> 00:33:43.606
but at
considerable elevation.

00:33:44.982 --> 00:33:46.526
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Sergeant Lope...

00:33:46.734 --> 00:33:48.319
let's go find our ghost.

00:34:01.999 --> 00:34:03.918
<font color="#808080">(CREW CHATTERING INDISTINCTLY)</font>

00:34:15.930 --> 00:34:17.473
Nice place for
a log cabin.

00:34:18.141 --> 00:34:19.308
Jake would have loved this.

00:34:19.475 --> 00:34:21.102
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Hey, Danny...

00:34:21.269 --> 00:34:23.229
it's not such a bad landing
site after all, huh?

00:34:23.396 --> 00:34:25.189
We got the housing units
right over there...

00:34:25.356 --> 00:34:27.567
civic complex
beyond the burn.

00:34:27.734 --> 00:34:29.569
We've got access
to fresh water.

00:34:29.736 --> 00:34:31.738
We might have a spot
for a colony right here.

00:34:31.904 --> 00:34:32.947
We'll see.

00:34:33.114 --> 00:34:37.410
Oh, ye of little faith.

00:34:38.494 --> 00:34:40.997
He's insufferable.

00:34:41.205 --> 00:34:43.291
It's worse when
he's happy, right?

00:34:43.374 --> 00:34:44.375
<font color="#808080">(CHUCKLES)</font>

00:34:48.045 --> 00:34:49.505
This is wheat.

00:34:51.632 --> 00:34:52.800
Believe me. I know wheat.

00:34:54.385 --> 00:34:56.721
This is old,
but definitely cultivated.

00:34:58.765 --> 00:35:00.725
What are the odds of finding
human vegetation...

00:35:00.892 --> 00:35:02.393
this far from Earth?

00:35:02.560 --> 00:35:03.686
Very unlikely.

00:35:09.317 --> 00:35:10.818
Who planted it?

00:35:32.173 --> 00:35:33.633
<font color="#808080">(THUNDER RUMBLING)</font>

00:35:37.303 --> 00:35:38.387
Eat.

00:35:38.554 --> 00:35:39.782
<font color="#804040">TENNESSEE:</font>
Hey, babe. Try Alpha.

00:35:39.806 --> 00:35:41.891
<font color="#804040">FARIS:</font> <i>All right.
Alpha's up.</i>

00:35:43.935 --> 00:35:46.687
Nothing. Give Beta a shot.

00:35:47.146 --> 00:35:49.607
<font color="#804040">FARIS:</font> <i>Beta up.</i>

00:35:49.774 --> 00:35:51.067
It's not doing shit.

00:35:51.692 --> 00:35:53.778
Is there really no way
to boost the signal?

00:35:53.945 --> 00:35:56.739
Not without going offline,
and recycling the cells.

00:35:56.906 --> 00:35:58.825
<font color="#804040">TENNESSEE:</font> <i>How long's
that gonna take?</i>

00:35:58.991 --> 00:36:01.244
I don't know. Few hours.

00:36:01.661 --> 00:36:03.996
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Keep up the pace.
Stay close.

00:36:04.163 --> 00:36:05.164
<font color="#804040">KARINE:</font> Chris.

00:36:05.331 --> 00:36:06.332
<font color="#804040">ROSENTHAL:</font> Hold up.

00:36:06.499 --> 00:36:08.584
<font color="#804040">KARINE:</font> I think
I wanna stay here.

00:36:09.585 --> 00:36:10.945
This might be
a good place to start

00:36:11.003 --> 00:36:12.255
a full ecology workup.

00:36:12.421 --> 00:36:14.340
You can pick me up
on the way back.

00:36:14.423 --> 00:36:15.466
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Sergeant?

00:36:15.550 --> 00:36:18.511
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Yeah, that's okay.
Ledward, stay with Karine.

00:36:18.678 --> 00:36:21.138
Meet back here in four hours.
Keep your comm open.

00:36:21.305 --> 00:36:23.391
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Behave yourself
with my wife.

00:36:23.558 --> 00:36:25.118
<font color="#804040">LEDWARD:</font> <font color="#808080">(CHUCKLES)</font>
You got it, Captain.

00:36:25.226 --> 00:36:26.435
<font color="#804040">KARINE:</font> Come on.

00:36:26.561 --> 00:36:28.354
<font color="#808080">(ALL PANTING)</font>

00:36:28.855 --> 00:36:30.481
<font color="#808080">(THUNDER RUMBLING)</font>

00:36:45.121 --> 00:36:46.831
Something passed
overhead here.

00:36:48.541 --> 00:36:50.084
Cut the tops off
the trees.

00:36:51.544 --> 00:36:53.880
Well, it had to be huge.

00:36:54.505 --> 00:36:56.966
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Well,
whatever it is...

00:36:57.133 --> 00:36:58.801
it's up there.

00:37:04.098 --> 00:37:05.558
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font> You hear that?

00:37:05.725 --> 00:37:06.809
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> What?

00:37:07.643 --> 00:37:08.728
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font> Nothing.

00:37:09.937 --> 00:37:12.523
No birds, no animals.

00:37:13.941 --> 00:37:14.942
Nothing.

00:37:26.329 --> 00:37:27.955
Wait. Slowly.

00:37:28.122 --> 00:37:29.498
Okay.

00:37:35.671 --> 00:37:36.839
<font color="#804040">KARINE:</font> This will do.

00:37:38.132 --> 00:37:41.010
<font color="#804040">TENNESSEE:</font> Expedition Team,
do you read us?

00:37:42.511 --> 00:37:44.472
Mother's saying the ion
storm is getting worse.

00:37:44.639 --> 00:37:47.016
We're having a hell of
a time tracking you.

00:37:47.099 --> 00:37:48.100
<font color="#808080">(STATIC ON RADIO)</font>

00:37:48.184 --> 00:37:51.103
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> <i>We're getting
very close... target...</i>

00:37:52.688 --> 00:37:54.523
<i>...communication when
we get there. Okay?</i>

00:37:54.607 --> 00:37:55.691
Covenant?

00:37:56.859 --> 00:37:58.194
Damn it.

00:38:03.199 --> 00:38:04.325
P-three.

00:38:09.538 --> 00:38:11.040
I gotta take a leak.

00:38:12.792 --> 00:38:13.918
Don't be long.

00:39:08.723 --> 00:39:09.849
<font color="#804040">KARINE:</font> Ledward?

00:39:10.016 --> 00:39:11.142
<font color="#804040">LEDWARD:</font> Coming.

00:39:13.769 --> 00:39:14.770
<font color="#808080">(SPITS)</font>

00:39:20.901 --> 00:39:22.236
<font color="#808080">(ALL PANTING)</font>

00:39:35.958 --> 00:39:36.959
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Hey.

00:39:38.961 --> 00:39:40.796
What the fuck is this?

00:39:43.132 --> 00:39:45.342
It appears to be
some kind of vehicle.

00:40:02.485 --> 00:40:03.861
<font color="#808080">(ALL PANTING)</font>

00:40:10.785 --> 00:40:13.412
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Ankor, Cole.
Stay here.

00:40:13.579 --> 00:40:15.372
<font color="#804040">ANKOR:</font> Got it.
<font color="#804040">COLE:</font> Yes, sir.

00:40:16.040 --> 00:40:17.958
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Careful, guys.
Watch your step.

00:40:23.089 --> 00:40:25.049
<font color="#808080">(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS)</font>

00:40:31.263 --> 00:40:33.599
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font> Captain.
Over here.

00:40:35.976 --> 00:40:37.412
You got a lock on the transmission,
Walter?

00:40:37.436 --> 00:40:38.479
<font color="#804040">WALTER:</font> This way.

00:40:39.271 --> 00:40:41.232
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Let's go.
Stick together.

00:40:41.482 --> 00:40:42.858
Do you see this shit?

00:40:49.073 --> 00:40:50.324
<font color="#808080">(PANTING)</font>

00:40:58.874 --> 00:40:59.874
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Tom.

00:40:59.917 --> 00:41:00.918
Come on, keep up.

00:41:01.085 --> 00:41:02.461
<font color="#804040">HALLETT:</font>
All right, I'm coming.

00:41:05.548 --> 00:41:06.757
<font color="#808080">(PANTING)</font>

00:41:09.301 --> 00:41:10.344
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

00:41:11.220 --> 00:41:12.471
Are you okay?

00:41:12.638 --> 00:41:14.014
Yeah, I'm fine.

00:41:14.974 --> 00:41:16.892
<font color="#808080">(LEDWARD BREATHING HEAVILY)</font>

00:41:37.204 --> 00:41:38.205
<font color="#804040">ROSENTHAL:</font> God.

00:41:39.623 --> 00:41:41.292
They were giants.

00:41:41.458 --> 00:41:45.087
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> At least
statues of giants.

00:41:49.550 --> 00:41:50.843
"Dr. E. Shaw."

00:41:52.469 --> 00:41:53.846
<font color="#804040">WALTER:</font>
Dr. Elizabeth Shaw.

00:41:55.973 --> 00:41:57.850
She was
Chief Science Officer...

00:41:58.017 --> 00:41:59.727
of the <i>Prometheus.</i>

00:42:00.060 --> 00:42:01.770
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font> The ship
that disappeared.

00:42:02.229 --> 00:42:04.857
Precisely.
10 years ago.

00:42:06.775 --> 00:42:08.319
Weyland Industries.

00:42:09.111 --> 00:42:10.821
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font> This isn't
a Weyland ship.

00:42:15.242 --> 00:42:17.077
Dr. Shaw.

00:42:17.995 --> 00:42:19.747
How did she end up here?

00:42:23.459 --> 00:42:25.299
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Sergeant Lope,
can I get a light on this?

00:42:25.336 --> 00:42:26.837
Over here.
<font color="#804040">ROSENTHAL:</font> Be careful.

00:42:27.004 --> 00:42:28.005
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> Yeah.

00:42:28.547 --> 00:42:29.548
Oh.

00:42:30.507 --> 00:42:31.550
Oh, wow.

00:42:31.675 --> 00:42:32.676
Jesus.

00:42:33.385 --> 00:42:34.386
Whoa.

00:42:35.971 --> 00:42:37.556
Oram, behind you.
Move.

00:42:49.902 --> 00:42:51.654
<font color="#808080">(DISTORTED SINGING)</font>
<i>Home</i>

00:42:51.820 --> 00:42:54.782
<i>Take me home</i>

00:42:54.949 --> 00:42:57.201
<i>To the place</i>

00:42:59.578 --> 00:43:00.871
<i>West Virginia...</i>

00:43:02.206 --> 00:43:03.415
<i>mountain momma</i>

00:43:03.582 --> 00:43:04.959
I think we found
our source.

00:43:08.212 --> 00:43:09.338
<font color="#804040">ROSENTHAL:</font> Yeah.

00:43:09.421 --> 00:43:11.090
<font color="#808080">(SHAW CONTINUES
DISTORTED SINGING)</font>

00:43:11.548 --> 00:43:13.300
What the hell was
she doing out here?

00:43:15.469 --> 00:43:17.388
Poor thing.

00:43:18.097 --> 00:43:19.932
<font color="#808080">(LEDWARD
BREATHING HEAVILY)</font>

00:43:21.058 --> 00:43:22.643
<font color="#808080">(COUGHING)</font>

00:43:23.644 --> 00:43:24.895
<font color="#804040">LEDWARD:</font>
I have to sit down.

00:43:25.437 --> 00:43:27.147
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTS)</font>
I have to sit down.

00:43:27.314 --> 00:43:29.358
<font color="#808080">(EXHALES DEEPLY)</font>
I'm sorry.

00:43:29.525 --> 00:43:31.360
I don't know
what's wrong with me.

00:43:31.527 --> 00:43:33.445
Just look at me.

00:43:35.990 --> 00:43:37.032
<font color="#808080">(CHOKING)</font>
I can't breathe.

00:43:38.075 --> 00:43:39.868
<font color="#808080">(COUGHING)</font>
Stay calm.

00:43:41.412 --> 00:43:42.871
I'll be right back.

00:43:42.955 --> 00:43:44.540
<font color="#808080">(LEDWARD GROANING)</font>

00:43:45.541 --> 00:43:47.459
<font color="#804040">KARINE:</font> Captain Oram.
Come in.

00:43:48.711 --> 00:43:50.296
<i>Come in.
Chris, it's Karine.</i>

00:43:50.754 --> 00:43:51.755
What? Yes?

00:43:51.922 --> 00:43:53.507
<i>We have an issue.</i>

00:43:53.674 --> 00:43:54.967
<i>We're heading back
to the Lander.</i>

00:43:55.050 --> 00:43:56.802
<i>Repeat.
We're returning to the Lander.</i>

00:43:56.969 --> 00:43:58.804
Is everything okay?

00:43:58.971 --> 00:44:01.849
<i>Ledward is sick.
We're heading back.</i>

00:44:02.016 --> 00:44:04.852
<i>Faris, you get that?
Prep the Med Bay, okay?</i>

00:44:05.019 --> 00:44:06.162
Will do, Karine.
What's going on?

00:44:06.186 --> 00:44:08.188
<i>Please, just do it.
We'll be there soon.</i>

00:44:08.355 --> 00:44:09.606
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> <i>Daniels, come in.</i>

00:44:09.773 --> 00:44:11.483
<i>We're heading back.</i>

00:44:14.278 --> 00:44:15.714
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font> <i>What's going on?</i>
<font color="#804040">ORAM:</font> <i>I don't know.</i>

00:44:15.738 --> 00:44:17.156
It's something
about, uh, Ledward.

00:44:19.283 --> 00:44:21.910
They're coming.
Let's move.

00:44:24.955 --> 00:44:25.956
<font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

00:44:26.665 --> 00:44:28.584
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font> Guys!
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> Tom!

00:44:28.751 --> 00:44:31.337
What's going on, man?
Hey. Are you all right?

00:44:31.503 --> 00:44:33.589
Talk to me. Look at me.
<font color="#808080">(GRUNTING)</font>

00:44:33.756 --> 00:44:35.632
You all right?
<font color="#804040">HALLETT:</font> Yeah, I'm okay.

00:44:35.799 --> 00:44:37.634
Can you walk?
Yeah.

00:44:37.801 --> 00:44:40.095
Okay, let's go. Let's get
the fuck out of here.

00:44:40.262 --> 00:44:41.638
All right.

00:44:43.349 --> 00:44:46.101
Babe, are we talking
quarantine protocols?

00:44:46.268 --> 00:44:48.270
<font color="#804040">FARIS:</font> <i>I don't know,
but she said that</i>

00:44:48.354 --> 00:44:50.189
<i>Ledward was bleeding...</i>

00:44:50.356 --> 00:44:52.024
and to prepare the Med Bay.

00:44:52.191 --> 00:44:53.317
<font color="#804040">TENNESSEE:</font> Bleeding?

00:44:53.484 --> 00:44:55.694
<font color="#804040">FARIS:</font> <i>Yeah, I know,
that's what I thought...</i>

00:44:55.861 --> 00:44:56.987
Faris, you're breaking up.

00:44:57.112 --> 00:44:58.673
<font color="#808080">(STAMMERS)</font> We can't hear you,
can you repeat?

00:44:58.697 --> 00:44:59.698
<i>I don't know from what,</i>

00:44:59.782 --> 00:45:01.784
<i>I don't know
how serious it is.</i>

00:45:01.950 --> 00:45:03.619
<i>She sounded scared.</i>

00:45:03.786 --> 00:45:06.205
<font color="#804040">KARINE:</font> <i>Faris, where are you?
Come on, I need your help!</i>

00:45:08.457 --> 00:45:10.292
Faris, where are you?

00:45:10.459 --> 00:45:12.294
We're here. Come in!
<font color="#808080">(GASPING)</font>

00:45:13.545 --> 00:45:15.381
Ledward, come on.
<font color="#808080">(WEAKLY)</font> I can't.

00:45:15.547 --> 00:45:18.801
Almost there, you see?
Straight ahead.

00:45:18.967 --> 00:45:21.720
Faris! Get over here!

00:45:21.887 --> 00:45:23.514
Come on, I need your help!
<font color="#808080">(PANTING)</font>

00:45:24.306 --> 00:45:26.475
<font color="#808080">(LEDWARD COUGHING)</font>

00:45:27.476 --> 00:45:29.311
<font color="#808080">(LEDWARD GASPING)</font>

00:45:34.525 --> 00:45:36.026
Fucking help me!

00:45:38.362 --> 00:45:39.488
Help me.

00:45:39.655 --> 00:45:41.156
<font color="#808080">(BREATHING SHAKILY)</font>

00:45:44.076 --> 00:45:45.796
<font color="#804040">KARINE:</font> Stay up, Ledward.
<font color="#808080">(LEDWARD WHEEZING)</font>

00:45:47.496 --> 00:45:48.736
<font color="#804040">FARIS:</font> Get him
to the Med Bay...

00:45:48.831 --> 00:45:50.311
<i>and touch nothing
on your way through.</i>

00:45:53.877 --> 00:45:56.672
<font color="#804040">KARINE:</font> Faris, get over here!
Come on!

00:45:57.506 --> 00:45:58.590
Go!
