What the fuck!
<font color="#808080">(ALL EXCLAIM IN DISGUST)</font>

00:51:40.015 --> 00:51:41.516
<font color="#808080">(BREATHING HEAVILY)</font>

00:51:43.393 --> 00:51:44.519
Ugh.

00:51:44.728 --> 00:51:46.354
<font color="#808080">(ALL GASPING)</font>

