Daniels, are you okay?
Yeah!

00:53:43.805 --> 00:53:45.015
<font color="#804040">COLE:</font> What the fuck was that?

00:53:45.557 --> 00:53:47.350
<font color="#804040">LOPE:</font> We are okay.
<font color="#808080">(ALIEN SCREECHES)</font>

