00:53:57.944 --> 00:53:59.195
Get off!

00:54:00.405 --> 00:54:01.698
<font color="#808080">(ROSENTHAL GRUNTING)</font>

00:54:04.659 --> 00:54:06.077
<font color="#808080">(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)</font>

00:54:06.161 --> 00:54:07.203
<font color="#808080">(SCREAMS)</font>

00:54:07.287 --> 00:54:08.455
<font color="#808080">(HIGH-PITCHED RINGING)</font>

00:54:26.348 --> 00:54:27.641
<font color="#804040">MAN:</font> Follow me.

00:54:31.102 --> 00:54:32.437
<font color="#804040">DANIELS:</font>
I'll get the captain.

