01:40:46.291 --> 01:40:48.127
<font color="#808080">(WHISK CLANKING)</font>

01:40:57.302 --> 01:40:59.430
<font color="#808080">(DOORBELL CHIMES)</font>
Yeah.

01:41:02.474 --> 01:41:03.475
Evening.

